      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1778005395333,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Odata ventity\n- no dupe\n- data resides in fno\n    no redundency\n- batch job to pull in bg\n\ncons:\nnetwork call for each crud.***",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Odata ventity\n- no dupe\n- data resides in fno\n    no redundency\n- batch job to pull in bg\n\ncons:\nnetwork call for each crud.***",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "hH5jEJwgCk-qtJSc5MncI",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1021.0172693864254,
      "y": 925.2657319866721,
      "width": 498.3994445800781,
      "height": 80,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aH",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 685557022,
      "version": 114,
      "versionNonce": 1943989726,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777787973206,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "what is contract\n\nLegal/billing agreement with a customer. Contains billing method \n(T&M vs Fixed Price), payment terms, currency.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "what is contract\n\nLegal/billing agreement with a customer. Contains billing method \n(T&M vs Fixed Price), payment terms, currency.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "PcRia48SWacjNirKyQOdI",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 991.8328821793941,
      "y": 1033.6970064007346,
      "width": 749.0555419921875,
      "height": 140,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aI",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 899039710,
      "version": 91,
      "versionNonce": 1136755230,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777787973206,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Customer (Account)\n  └── Project Contract          — \"We'll do X work for $Y\"\n        └── Contract Line       — \"Specifically, this scope for this price\"\n              └── Project       — \"The actual work plan\"\n                    └── Task    — \"Individual work items\"\n                          └── Resource Assignment — \"Person X does Task Y\"\n                                └── Time Entry   — \"Person X worked 8 hrs on Task Y on Monday\"",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Customer (Account)\n  └── Project Contract          — \"We'll do X work for $Y\"\n        └── Contract Line       — \"Specifically, this scope for this price\"\n              └── Project       — \"The actual work plan\"\n                    └── Task    — \"Individual work items\"\n                          └── Resource Assignment — \"Person X does Task Y\"\n                                └── Time Entry   — \"Person X worked 8 hrs on Task Y on Monday\"",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "kMwEp-WeQVCoAUGiiGB8R",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 131.054965453706,
      "y": 576.0856636239545,
      "width": 559.6954345703125,
      "height": 380,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aJ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 447829506,
      "version": 796,
      "versionNonce": 1036700098,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777788704955,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "when a project was created, it was needed to be mapped to a contract\n    - fetch a contract from FnO (same userid, same scope)\n    - user picks one, entity gets created in CE\ncreate contract line:\n    simple, no fno sync needed\npull contract line :\n    sync from fno, \n    100s of contract line\nper contract line cld:\n    upto 10k total cld : exposed a button to pull async\n    batch job\n        its a routine runner that runs your code\n        your code should handle dupes and all else and return status\n            retry, succeed, fail, partial\n        it lets you store cursor for each run metadata, upto you how to\n            choose cursor\n        resolved idempotency\n        configurable batch size\n        ...where x.created_at > <time>",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "when a project was created, it was needed to be mapped to a contract\n    - fetch a contract from FnO (same userid, same scope)\n    - user picks one, entity gets created in CE\ncreate contract line:\n    simple, no fno sync needed\npull contract line :\n    sync from fno, \n    100s of contract line\nper contract line cld:\n    upto 10k total cld : exposed a button to pull async\n    batch job\n        its a routine runner that runs your code\n        your code should handle dupes and all else and return status\n            retry, succeed, fail, partial\n        it lets you store cursor for each run metadata, upto you how to\n            choose cursor\n        resolved idempotency\n        configurable batch size\n        ...where x.created_at > <time>",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "LAutqPGnU0Pct6bNqwhJS",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -569.879975950673,
      "y": 634.2416347277665,
      "width": 324.22369384765625,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
