      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1778571183042,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "HOW\n\nDUAL write:\n1. user cruds in fno table\n    and in staging table\n2. batch job next run picks up\n3. copies new entries to CE\n\nhow skips done rows?\n    status col (sourcedone\n        retry, failed, succeed)\nIssue : \n    in step 1 user might miss\nor paritially write entries\n    might be dupe entries\n    batch job interval - not on demand\n    extra stagiing table\n    ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "HOW\n\nDUAL write:\n1. user cruds in fno table\n    and in staging table\n2. batch job next run picks up\n3. copies new entries to CE\n\nhow skips done rows?\n    status col (sourcedone\n        retry, failed, succeed)\nIssue : \n    in step 1 user might miss\nor paritially write entries\n    might be dupe entries\n    batch job interval - not on demand\n    extra stagiing table\n    ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
